		<span id="title-175693969" class="story-title"> <a   href="//games.slashdot.org/story/24/12/18/136229/microsoft-abandons-xbox-exclusivity-in-risky-gaming-strategy-shift">Microsoft Abandons Xbox Exclusivity in Risky Gaming Strategy Shift</a></span>

		
		
		<!--<span class="comments commentcnt-175693969" >48</span>-->
		

		
